*Proposed Changes*

• Fixes <https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/issues/7417|#7417>
• Users can select multiple images at once
• Use jspdf to merge multiple uploaded images into pdf

@ohcnetwork/care-fe-code-reviewers

*Summary by CodeRabbit*

• *New Features*  
   • Added ability to combine multiple image files into a single PDF during upload.  
   • Introduced PDF generation functionality for file uploads.  
   • New option "Combine Files To PDF" available in the user interface.  
   • New messages for file conversion progress and success, along with an error message for PDF generation failures.
• *Dependencies*  
   • Added `jspdf` library for PDF creation.  
   • Downgraded `input-otp` library version.
